Capital Gains for Personal = Possible tax Benefit

Capital Gains for Businesses = No difference in tax rates

LLC / domestic partnership must file an information return, unless it neither receives gross income nor pays or incurs any amount treated as a deduction or credit for federal income tax purposes
Note that if you don’t need to file for federal purposes you might still need to file and pay a tax at the state level
A Corporation needs to file a tax return even if it had no activity at all

Crypto transaction for an individual is usually capital in nature (capital gains)

Crypto transactions for artists, business, creators are usually ordinary in nature (ordinary income tax)
Taxes taken from paycheck do not mean that you don’t owe additional taxes.
Estimated taxes are due during the year not just April 15th
An extension is an extension to file NOT and extension to pay

Even if no taxes are due you still need to file on time to avoid penalties and interest.
